<br>
Well, as Sar said, it was the straw that broke the camel's back. Why did Shintou react that way to Ankles post and not to the hundred other far worse messages he's received? Hard to say.... Ankles is well-liked and well-respected by many people--perhaps even by Shintou. Maybe that's why he took her opinion so personally.... /shrug<br>
